{"word":"ἀνακαλύπτω","slug":"ἀνακαλύπτω","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b><el>ἀναϰαλύπτω</el></b> [<el><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:ἀνά\">ἀνά</a>, ϰαλύτω</el>] ‘remove a covering’, <b><i>unveil</i></b> in imagery of removal of that which impedes perception of God’s activity in connection with Christ <b><a href='B:540 3:14'>2 Cor 3:14</a>, <a href='B:540 3:18'>18</a>.</b> <center id=\"nav_bottom\"> <a id=\"left_arrow\" href=\"S:ἀνακαίνωσις\">&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;</a> <a id=\"bottom_home\" href=\"S:#1.Table of Contents\">&emsp;&emsp;</a> <a id=\"right_arrow\" href=\"S:ἀνακάμπτω\">&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;</a> </center> "}]}